# Normalise line endings in the coverage ledger so git diff --exit-code
# in CI produces a clean result regardless of contributor core.autocrlf
# settings. Without this, a contributor with autocrlf=false on Windows
# can commit CRLF line endings; the CI runner rewrites the file as LF;
# the diff step reports spurious drift indistinguishable from real content
# changes.
*.json text eol=lf
